    "However, this alignment may lead to risks of value totalitarianism and ideological monopoly.",
    "If the ethical frameworks imposed on LLMs are overly rigid or reflect a narrow set of values, these models may reinforce a singular worldview, which can marginalize alternative perspectives and suppress cultural diversity.",
    "The concentration of ideological power in the hands of those controlling the alignment process may stifle innovation and critical thinking while reinforcing existing social inequalities.",
    "These concerns highlight the need for comprehensive oversight.",
    "The moral growth of LLMs is not solely a scientific issue but also a philosophical and ethical one."
